article.headline: Rice defeats Northwestern State 76-51
article.description: — Max Fiedler had 16 points in Rice's 76-51 victory against Northwestern State on Saturday.
article.story: NATCHITOCHES, La. -- — Max Fiedler had 16 points in Rice's 76-51 victory against Northwestern State on Saturday. Fiedler added eight rebounds and five assists for the Owls (5-6). Mekhi Mason scored 14 points. Justin Wilson finished with 10 points and two blocks for the Demons (1-10). The loss was the Demons' 10th straight. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
